author: ekoneil
msg: Add NetUI BVT that tests the use of scriptlet from a .tag file used in various content spots in the data grid.
This test also ensures that the getJspContext().getOut().write(String) sends output to the correct output buffer and that the output shows up in the right place in the response.
Also switch the dataGrid tag onto the getJspContext() method rather than getPageContext().
